        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4075784217" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16287529051521725610">Another re-read, and an excellent one. Among other things it illustrates the problems that technology can introduce into a society. While one-sided in this regard (mainly, I think, because the technologies being introduced are ones with which we are familiar and consider commonplace), it makes it obvious that there IS another side, and one which must be taken into account.<br/><br/>I do enjoy this series; there are some issues I have with the series, but overall it&apos;s very enjoyable and worth reading.</span>
  <span id="freeText16287529051521725610" style="display:none">Another re-read, and an excellent one. Among other things it illustrates the problems that technology can introduce into a society. While one-sided in this regard (mainly, I think, because the technologies being introduced are ones with which we are familiar and consider commonplace), it makes it obvious that there IS another side, and one which must be taken into account.<br /><br />I do enjoy this series; there are some issues I have with the series, but overall it's very enjoyable and worth reading.</span>
