<div id="review_2288932910" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2288932910" />
    <a title="Jan  Bond" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/46540877-jan-bond"><img alt="Jan  Bond" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2288932910?book_show_action=true">Feb 08, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jan  Bond" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jan  Bond" href="/user/show/46540877-jan-bond">Jan  Bond</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/6081682-the-skies-of-pern">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2288932910" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2292359396089571599">I have read every book McCaffrey has written. It takes a real wordsmith to make me want to read everything someone has authored and that is what McCaffrey is - a wonderful wordsmith. I have all of her books in print and many in digital format. I read them when each one was released in paperback and am so enjoying rereading these tomes. Her books draw you into the worlds she creates - as a non-author I am truly amazed that someone can do that with only the written word. The Skies of Pern is a wel</span>
  <span id="freeText2292359396089571599" style="display:none">I have read every book McCaffrey has written. It takes a real wordsmith to make me want to read everything someone has authored and that is what McCaffrey is - a wonderful wordsmith. I have all of her books in print and many in digital format. I read them when each one was released in paperback and am so enjoying rereading these tomes. Her books draw you into the worlds she creates - as a non-author I am truly amazed that someone can do that with only the written word. The Skies of Pern is a well done conclusion to the the series. I liked the part where the dragon riders have found a new craft and hold now that read threat of "threads" has been resolved. My only negative is that McCaffrey has passed and will no longer produce wonderful worlds to explore.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2292359396089571599" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


